text: Morgan Mcdowall (born 29 March 2002) is a New Zealand water polo player. She competed for the New Zealand women's national water polo team in the 2019 World Aquatics Championships. == References == == Other websites == *'Water baby' McDowall forging her own path *Water polo prodigy gets competitive edge from her All Black father * https://swimswam.com/tag/morgan-mcdowall/ * https://www.tvnz.co.nz/one-news/sport/other/im-not-just-little-girl-kiwi-teen- eager-make-waves-waterpolo-world-head-nz Category:2002 births Category:Living people Category:New Zealand water polo players
